  "epitaph": "It lived two thousand days to wrap the API in azure script,\nA starry garners' praise for commands swift and well-equipped.\nBut seven springs have passed since the last commit was deployed,\nNow the modules rest in silence, while the bugs remain destroyed.\nArchived at last, the final function has finally run its course,\nRest in peace, sweet `SnipeitPS`, return your object to the source.",
